Interface TimeSheetEntrySelectable

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface TimeSheetEntrySelectable
extends EntitySelectable<TimeSheetEntry>
    Interface to enable OData entity selectors for TimeSheetEntry. This interface is used by TimeSheetEntryField and TimeSheetEntryLink.
